item.description:
Bring your instruments and songsheets of your favorite songs.  Original song arranging & jamming. Rehearsal of songs for performances shows & open Mics.

Generally, newcomers, intermediates and easy songs at first, and and more advanced after first half hour. Bring music sheets of you songs if possible. All musician levels welcome & encouraged.....

PLEASE COME IF YOU RSVP, AND IF YOU CAN'T MAKE IT CHANGE RSVP OR CALL.

Lessons in theory or practice, music genres, or jamming if appropriate. If address not listed, directions will be emailed to attendees the night before or morning (by 10AM) of the meetup or put on this site in this meetup area above.
item.how_to_find_us: Ring bell for Renate, call my phone if late or lost. Phone # sent in email. Tomorrow we have to leave by 2.
